{"tid":2369110,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–你敢唔敢食？","createTime":"2021-01-16T21:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T07:55:35.000Z","uid":38861,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bba1c8b10eb5b0cee34cf9a9587b3c3fdfa00a96","tid":2369110,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T21:42:19.000Z","msg":"癌細胞有各種手段逃避我們身體免疫系統的追捕，其中之一的手段就是在表面上表達名為PDL1的蛋白質。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GfCCmWt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGfCCmWt.jpg&h=cdbbca91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n免疫系統細胞表面的PD1蛋白質與PDL1確認的話，便不會追殺癌細胞，任由惡勢力增長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）用抗體阻擋PD1，導致免疫系統細胞不再受癌細胞蒙騙，繼而懂得消滅癌細胞，就是免疫治療的精髓所在。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2uk39S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2uk39S.jpg&h=2c79c75b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只不過，若癌細胞沒有表達PDL1蛋白質的話，此方法便不奏效。<br />\n<br />\n而且就算癌細胞真的是有表達PDL1蛋白質，此方法對某一些病人亦不太見效。<br />\n<br />\n免疫治療延伸閱讀:<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/471125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F471125&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=202e74d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/471125</a><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）有研究發現，腸道的細菌群組能夠影響免疫治療的效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMcbrog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMcbrog.jpg&h=386f00a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此，有臨床研究嘗試將對免疫治療有效的病人的腸道細菌，以手術及口服糞便藥丸的方法移植到對免疫治療無效的病人腸道，試驗能否增強免疫治療的效用。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）利用糞便移植手段，原先對免疫治療無效的病人亦出現顯著的效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXedEJk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXedEJk.png&h=e1e79b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是次研究共有五名試驗者，有三名出現了正面效果。其中一名病患在半個月後，身上的皮膚癌更是完全消失。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=a9451a89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=ed415bf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2020/12/09/science.abb5920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2020%2F12%2F09%2Fscience.abb5920&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=41c22ea7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2020/12/09/science.abb5920</a>"},{"pid":"bd28ab25097b5446f3eff59e8d2de8c31b2c68b3","tid":2369110,"uid":34119,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T21:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"xx-large\">🤎💩</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/dc3/ad2/dc3ad21aa6cf6eab022516d6bbe9d69113b1e25d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fdc